Description: HyprGlassShell greeter for greetd
  HyprGlassShell greeter for greetd login manager. A modern, Material Design 3
  inspired greeter interface built with Quickshell for Wayland compositors.
  .
  Targets the Hyprland compositor with automatic configuration. Features session selection, user
  authentication, and dynamic theming.
